# SarojJaprel.com.np Website

This is the source code for my personal website.  
It is hosted on **GitHub Pages** and connected to my custom domain via **Cloudflare**.

## 🌐 Live Site
- [sarojjaprel.com.np](https://sarojjaprel.com.np)

## 📂 Project Files
- `index.html` → Homepage
- `style.css` → Stylesheet
- `README.md` → Documentation

## 🚀 How to Deploy
1. Push this code to GitHub.
2. Enable **GitHub Pages** in repository settings.
3. Add your custom domain (`sarojjaprel.com.np`) in GitHub Pages.
4. Point your domain to GitHub Pages using Cloudflare DNS.

## 🛠️ Built With
- HTML5
- CSS3
- GitHub Pages
- Cloudflare DNS

